###############################################################################
### gtranslator README R 0.16
###############################################################################
	gtranslator will be a translation-supporting programm for the Gnome
	project . It is offering little funtionability yet but it will be 
	more expandable later on . 
	
	If you've got this from CVS , you've got to read the INSTALL.CVS
	file in order to get the ./configure script etc.
	
	Have a look at it and you'll see that it isn't/couldn't be finished 
	or really satisfying till this moment .
 
	If you want to have a usable version wait till R 0.2(0) , I think till 
	this version it should be ready-to-use .

	Pay my attention ( huh, how does this work .. ) by adding your wishes 
	to the TODO file in the CVS tree .

	(Fatih Demir)->(kabalak@gmx.net)->(2000-04-19)
###############################################################################
